==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tailzie
<hw>Tail"zie</hw> <pr>(-z⟦icr⟧ ⟦or⟧ -y⟦icr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[F. <ets>tailler</ets> to cut. See <er>Tail</er> a
limitation.]</ety> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>An entailment or deed
whereby the legal course of succession is cut off, and an arbitrary one
substituted.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>tailzee</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tain</ent>⟦br⟧
